<item>
            <title>[LU-10953] sanity/300k fails on local small setups</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10953</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity/300k constantly fails on small filesystems due to huge transaction (few thousand blocks). the test simulates creation of a directory with 512 stripes. this is fine on a regular setup with large journal, but not on a small one. besides own failure all subsequent tests have no chance.&lt;/p&gt;

